textBoxes.content:
<text-box>
  <inline color="#f9f8f3" font-size="16px">Venture Global - WWP 8 Week Lookahead</inline>
</text-box>

calculatedFields.name: 3 Weeks Ahead WEDate
calculatedFields.expression:
ifelse(extract('WD',now()) = 1, 
ifelse(weekend = truncDate('WK',now()) 
 OR weekend = addDateTime(7,'DD',truncDate('WK',now())) 
 OR weekend = addDateTime(14,'DD',truncDate('WK',now())),'3 Weeks Ahead',NULL), 

ifelse(weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(7,'DD',now())) 
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(14,'DD',now())) 
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(21,'DD',now())),'3 Weeks Ahead',NULL))

calculatedFields.name: 6 Weeks Ahead WEDate
calculatedFields.expression:
ifelse(extract('WD',now()) = 1, 
ifelse(weekend = truncDate('WK',now()) 
 OR weekend = addDateTime(7,'DD',truncDate('WK',now())) 
 OR weekend = addDateTime(14,'DD',truncDate('WK',now()))
 OR weekend = addDateTime(21,'DD',truncDate('WK',now()))
 OR weekend = addDateTime(28,'DD',truncDate('WK',now()))
 OR weekend = addDateTime(35,'DD',truncDate('WK',now())),'6 Weeks Ahead',NULL), 

ifelse(weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(7,'DD',now())) 
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(14,'DD',now())) 
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(21,'DD',now()))
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(28,'DD',now()))
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(35,'DD',now()))
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(42,'DD',now())),'6 Weeks Ahead',NULL))

 OR weekend = addDateTime(42,'DD',truncDate('WK',now()))
 OR weekend = addDateTime(49,'DD',truncDate('WK',now())),'8 Weeks Ahead',NULL), 

ifelse(weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(7,'DD',now()))

 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(21,'DD',now()))
 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(28,'DD',now()))

 OR weekend = truncDate('WK',addDateTime(49,'DD',now()))

calculatedFields.name: Required Planned
calculatedFields.expression: ifelse(isNull({WWP Hours}),0,{WWP Hours}) - ifelse(isNull({Non Required Planned}),0,{Non Required Planned})
